# Pre-requisites

## Project Title

OptiCrop – Smart Agricultural Production Optimization System

## Introduction

The OptiCrop system requires various software tools, programming languages, libraries, and platforms to collect agricultural data, train machine learning models, and generate crop recommendations. The following prerequisites are necessary for successful development and deployment of the project.

## Hardware Requirements

* Processor: Intel Core i3 or above
* RAM: 4 GB minimum (8 GB recommended)
* Storage: 10 GB free disk space
* Internet Connection

## Software Requirements

### Operating System

* Windows 10/11
* Linux
* macOS

### Development Environment

* Visual Studio Code (VS Code)

### Programming Language

* Python 3.10 or above

### Version Control

* Git
* GitHub

## Python Libraries

### Data Processing

* Pandas
* NumPy

### Data Visualization

* Matplotlib
* Seaborn

### Machine Learning

* Scikit-learn

### Model Storage

* Pickle

### Web Application Development

* Streamlit

## Dataset Requirements

The system requires an agricultural dataset containing:

* Nitrogen (N)
* Phosphorous (P)
* Potassium (K)
* Temperature
* Humidity
* pH
* Rainfall
* Crop Label

## Tools Used

| Tool         | Purpose                 |
| ------------ | ----------------------- |
| VS Code      | Development Environment |
| Python       | Programming Language    |
| Git          | Version Control         |
| GitHub       | Source Code Management  |
| Streamlit    | Web Application         |
| Scikit-learn | Machine Learning        |
| Pandas       | Data Processing         |
| NumPy        | Numerical Computation   |
| Matplotlib   | Visualization           |

## Expected Outcome

After installing all prerequisites, the system will be ready for data collection, preprocessing, model training, crop prediction, and application deployment.

## Conclusion

The above prerequisites provide the necessary environment for developing and deploying the OptiCrop Smart Agricultural Production Optimization System efficiently.
